--- 0. Sweep methodology ---

grep -n -- '-match|-notmatch|-replace|-eq |-ne |-contains|-notcontains|
-like|-notlike|switch' plugins/sdd-domain/scripts/domain-review-precheck.ps1

Every hit was cross-checked against domain-review-precheck.sh's actual
bash/jq case-sensitivity semantics (bash `[[ =~ ]]`/`==` and jq `==`/test()
are always case-sensitive; no nocasematch anywhere in the .sh original).

